          "_note": "precondition GET against the REAL cluster_id — expect 200 now that the cluster is RUNNING; tolerate 4xx (optional+grouped) so a precondition hiccup does not abandon the cluster before teardown."
        },
        {
          "name": "aimlops-validate-namespaces",
